We adopt a quite different approach and regard the
minimization of the KS functional as a complex optim-
ization problem which can be solved by applying the
concept of simulated annealing, recently introduced by
Kirkpatrick, Gelatt, and Vecchi.i In this approach an
objective function O ((A3)) is minimized relative to the
